WEBVTT

01:15:07.608 --> 01:15:08.691
His name is Avira.

01:15:08.983 --> 01:15:09.983
Thirty years old.

01:15:10.816 --> 01:15:11.858
He's a single child.

01:15:12.983 --> 01:15:14.524
His father is a college professor.

01:15:14.941 --> 01:15:15.983
His mother is a housewife.

01:15:17.649 --> 01:15:18.858
The family is well-respected.

01:15:20.566 --> 01:15:24.191
After completing his M.Tech,
he worked for a company in Dubai.
